summary: Some subtle changes to Aela the Huntress.
descriptionHtml:
[color=green]Info[/color]
I really like Aela's face but I felt she needed a subtle facelift. I really didnt want to change the face too much because this char has a lot of character and personality, so hopefully I've made her more appealing while keeping her personality intact.

[color=green]Install[/color]
Simply install with NMM.
2 versions available, my Warpaint choice or original.

[color=green]Dark Face bug? Conflicts?[/color]
This is a very simple mod and 99.9% of issues can be corrected by sorting your load order properly.
If Aelas face doesnt look right/darker or has no warpaint simply use LOOT to sort your load order.
If problems persist force this mod to load after any other mods affecting Aela [i]in any way[/i], you can use tes5edit to check for conflicts. If problems still persist then you must have installed another mod that changes Aela's face specifically and will need to properly uninstall it to remove the files.


[color=green]Requirements[/color]
No other mods required.


[color=#e69138]Enjoy! And don't forget to endorse if you liked it![/color]

Feel free to add images!
[color=#e69138]If you liked this you might like my other mod,[/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/8331/?]Mjoll Facelift[/url]
author: Axeface
